name: #18. DOTTY "THE DOT" SCARLETTI
description:
Mysterious heiress to the Acme Buttons empire, with an accent one just cannot place. A carrot martini always in her paw. Can hold her liquor as well as anyone in The Mad Hatters Club. Meaning not that well.

"The more you take, the more you leave behind. What am I?"
"Feed me and I live, yet give me a drink and I die"
"What has hands but can not clap?"

'r' toggles auto-rotate. 'l' toggles cursor following.

Artist: Radarboy3000
